    <item>
      <title>Stifel与Lord Abbett建立最新私人信贷合作伙伴关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/stifel-and-lord-abbett-form-latest-private-credit-partnership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯蒂费尔金融公司 (Stifel Financial Corp.) 和 Lord Abbett &amp; Co. 正在联手组建一家私人信贷合资企业，这是投资银行和传统资产管理公司之间的最新合作，双方都试图在不断增长的 1.7 万亿美元资产类别中分得更大份额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/stifel-and-lord-abbett-form-latest-private-credit-partnership</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 13:36:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
